OL,3,C'Reckless' driver admits causing hit-
OL,4,Cand-run that left child critically
OL,5,Cinjured
OL,7,FAn 18-year-old man has pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto causing a crash in Bristol that
OL,9,Fleft a four-year-old boy in a critical
OL,10,Fcondition in hospital.
OL,12,FJames Doherty, of no fixed address,
OL,13,Fappeared at Bristol Magistrates' Court
OL,14,Fearlier today having been charged on
OL,15,FMonday 18 November.
OL,17,FHe pleaded guilty to causing serious
OL,18,Finjury by dangerous driving and was
OL,19,Fremanded into custody for sentencing
OL,20,Fat Bristol Crown Court on Tuesday 17
OL,21,FDecember.
