OL,3,C'Reckless' driver admits causing hit-
OL,4,Cand-run that left child critically
OL,5,Cinjured
OL,7,FIt follows a collision in Long Cross,
OL,8,Fnear the junction with Kings Weston
OL,9,FRoad, which happened shortly before
OL,10,F2pm on Sunday 17 November.
OL,12,FA car driven by Doherty left the road
OL,13,Fand collided with a four-year-old boy
OL,14,Fand a woman. He fled the scene and was
OL,15,Farrested later on Sunday afternoon.
OL,17,FThe four-year-old boy remains in
OL,18,Fhospital in a critical condition. His
OL,19,Ffamily continue to be supported by
OL,20,Fspecially trained officers.
