OL,5,Cinjured
OL,7,FThe woman, aged in her late teens,
OL,8,Falso sustained a leg injury which
OL,9,Frequired hospital treatment. She has
OL,10,Fsince been discharged to continue her
OL,11,Frecovery.
OL,13,FSerious collision investigator David
OL,14,FPaniccia-Brown said: "Doherty's
OL,15,Fdriving was utterly reckless and has
OL,16,Fleft a very young boy in hospital with
OL,17,Fincredibly serious injuries.
