OL,5,Cinjured
OL,7,F"His decision to drive in the manner
OL,8,Fhe did put lives at risk and his
OL,9,Fdecision to run away immediately after
OL,10,Fthe collision in an attempt to avoid
OL,11,Fthe consequences of his actions,
OL,12,Frather than try and help, were
OL,13,Fcowardly.
OL,15,F"Our thoughts remain with the boy's
OL,16,Ffamily who have been updated on this
OL,17,Fdevelopment and continue to be
OL,18,Fsupported by specially trained
OL,19,Fofficers.
