OL,7,F"I'd like to thank all the officers
OL,8,Finvolved in ensuring we were able to
OL,9,Fquickly put a strong case before the
OL,10,Fcourt and ensure this conviction."
OL,12,FNeighbourhood inspector Serena
OL,13,FSerjeant added: "We recognise the
OL,14,Fconcern this collision has caused
OL,15,Fwithin Lawrence Weston and officers
OL,16,Fhave been carrying out extra
OL,17,Freassurance patrols in the area since
OL,18,FSunday.
OL,20,F"If you have any worries or concerns
OL,21,Fthen please do approach an officer."
